 LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">knowledge, skills, and </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">confidence</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic"> to effectively manage their</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic"> own</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic"> health</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">. </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Being diagnosed with a </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">long-term</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> condition is a life-changing event which may involve changes in lifestyle and </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">require new </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">competenc</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ies</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> in</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">, for example,</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> medicines management</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 90pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 72pt; text-indent:-36pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">4</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">.3.2</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Fru