ily:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ing – a means </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">to self-administer dialysis</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> –</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> but the tariff acts as a disincentive because the needles </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">necessary </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">are more expensive than</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> the</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> sharp</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">er</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> needles used in staff-administered dialysis. </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">5</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">.0</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">              </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">What we have learned</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold"> about how to overcome these barriers</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 35.45pt; text-indent:-35.45pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">5</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">.1</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Creating a culture that supports person-centred care is a significant challenge</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">. </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Our programme teams </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">have </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">had to be creative and</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> flexible to overcome barriers.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> Support from senior leadership – up to trust board levels –</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> has been vital in </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">gaining traction.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 35.45pt; text-indent:-35.45pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 35.45pt; text-indent:-35.45pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">5</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">.2</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">              </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">Changing culture </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">and behaviours </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">among health professionals</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 35.45pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Health professi